OBCQL_QUERY_COLUMN.NAME: Received
OBCQL_QUERY_COLUMN.WHERECLAUSE_LEFT_PART: (select coalesce(sum(po.quantity),0) from ProcurementPOInvoiceMatch po where po.goodsShipmentLine is not null and po.salesOrderLine = ol)

OBCQL_QUERY_COLUMN.NAME: Pending
OBCQL_QUERY_COLUMN.WHERECLAUSE_LEFT_PART: (select ol.orderedQuantity-coalesce(sum(po2.quantity),0) from ProcurementPOInvoiceMatch po2 where po2.goodsShipmentLine is not null and po2.salesOrderLine = ol)
